Package: spcepc
Title: Predictive Maintenance and Integrated Process Control
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sameer", "Suman", email = "ss.sameer0101@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Simulates and evaluates integrated Engineering Process Control (EPC) 
    and Statistical Process Control (SPC). Based on the framework by Montgomery et al. (1994), 
    this package provides tools for modeling AR(1) industrial processes, simulating 
    Minimum Mean Square Error (MMSE) controllers, and applying Shewhart, EWMA, and CUSUM 
    charts to detect masked mechanical failures in automated manufacturing environments.
